N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 25.7 - Optional bar coding

State Regulations
A manufacturer is permitted to use bar coding which
provides the year, make, model, vehicle identification number, engine
identification number and either California or standard emissions equipment for
the vehicle described on the certificate of origin. Notes
